    "[1] demonstrated a work for traditional technique using Rule-based approach in order to build a system for the automatic detection of Named Entities(NEs) from tourist domain dataset.",
    "The accuracy acheived of 83% and 71% respectively which has been obtained by the algorithm while considering words with and without its repetition.Jumani et al. [16] investigated the issue of NER in the Sindhi Language and proposed a solution.",
    "The primary goal of the system is to identify and classify ten specific named entities.",
    "To achieve this, a rule-based approach [57] is employed for the NER system in Sindhi Language.",
    "They also explained how NER works for Sindhi language and provided necessary solutions as the system was developed to classify 10 different entities."
